hronous read methods of <xref:System.Diagnostics.Process.StandardOutput%2A> such as <xref:System.IO.StreamReader.Read%2A>, <xref:System.IO.StreamReader.ReadLine%2A>, or <xref:System.IO.StreamReader.ReadToEnd%2A>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
